high_descs: Turn around and go to the left side of the brown desk to the right of the window.
Pick up the pencil on the desk.
Turn right and move closer towards the desk.
Place the pencil in the glass bowl on the desk.
Pick up the glass bowl with the pencil in it.
Turn right and head to the other desk with the lamp on it.
Put the glass bowl with the pencil in it on the top right hand shelf on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move  the glass bowl containing a pencil from the desk near the window to the bookshelf on the other desk.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the bed and walk to the wooden desk on the right.
Pick up the white pencil from the left side of the desk.
Turn right and walk to the wooden desk on the left.
Put the pencil inside a clear bowl on the desk.
Pick up the clear bowl with the pencil inside from the desk.
Turn right and walk to the wooden desk on the left.
Put the bowl with the pencil inside on the top right shelf of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a pencil on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left across the room and head towards the table on your right.
Pick up the pencil at the edge of the table.
Turn around right and back to the table.
Drop the pencil on the transparent plate on the table.
Pick up the transparent plate from the table.
Turn right around the room and head towards the book shelf on your left.
Put the transparent plate in the book shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a transparent plate with pencil in a book shelf.
